This Repo contains all my electricity projects I have done in the past using linux and breadboard along with other components as needed.
Most projects involve wires, LEDs, battery, multimeter, resistors etc...
My projects might also include soldering of PCB's.
Projects
This is a project that involves four LEDs that can function in a pattern in varying speeds and brightness.
